Package: CNTools
Version: 1.0.2
Title: Convert segment data so that classification can be performed 
  on copy number data 
Author: Jianhua Zhang
Maintainer: J. Zhang <jzhang@jimmy.harvard.edu>
Depends: methods, stats, genefilter, genefilter
Description: This package provides tools to convert the output of 
  segmentation analysis using DNAcopy to a matrix structure so that 
  classifications can be applied to segmented copy number data 
Keyword: copy number
biocViews: Platform, Microarray
License: LGPL
ZipData: no
LazyLoad: no
